Newport Village caters to those who prefer an upscale, relaxed community with a helpful staff and premium amenities and features. Located at 8901 Colorado Blvd., we’re within easy distance of shopping, dining, recreation, entertainment, medical facilities, business hubs, and transportation options. Our floor plans feature apartments in Thornton with one, two, and three bedrooms, in addition to our popular one-bedroom plus loft option.  
A Beautiful Place to Call Home
Our community is pet-friendly and offers a dog park, a beautiful heated swimming pool, and a playground. Here you’ll enjoy 24-hour emergency maintenance, high-speed Internet, walking trails, on-site maintenance, and central air conditioning. Our apartments have been carefully detailed to provide the utmost in comfort and convenience for our residents. If you’ve been searching for a great place to call home, look no further than Newport Village.  
