Spacious Apartments for Rent in Thornton, Colorado
Newport Village offers a variety of roomy apartments in Thornton with one- and two-bedroom options, along with an option for a one-bedroom home plus a den. Our layouts include options for bi-level apartment homes, fireplaces, and bar areas, and you’ll find large patios, vaulted ceilings, open-concept kitchens, expansive living areas, and more.
          
Expansive Spaces and Unique Options
Our floor plan options range in size from 633 square feet for our one-bedroom, one-bathroom options to 856 square feet for our two-bedroom, two-bath layouts. Options include a variety of unique features, including wrap around porches, walk-in closets, separate laundry rooms, washers and dryers, and many others. With so many different options to choose from and such a great variety of amenities and features included, we’re sure that Newport Village has just the floor plan you’ve been searching for.
