We Offer Beauty, Tranquility, and Premium Access to Every Convenience You Could Ask For


Ideally Located Apartments for Rent in Thornton, CO
Just minutes from downtown Thornton is Newport Village – an upscale apartment community filled with convenient amenities and features designed with you in mind! One of our best features is our location; we offer easy access to major highways, roads, and interstates like I-25, I-270, and Highways 36 and 44. Our community puts our residents in a location that makes accessing all the best of Thornton easy!
The Convenience of Newport Village
Our Thornton, CO apartments are located on Colorado Blvd. near shopping centers and stores, restaurants and diners, parks and recreational areas, entertainment venues, and much more. You’ll be near banks, businesses, post offices, schools and universities, and movie theaters, among other attractions.
          Discover your place at Newport Village today!











