Did you know?

Not only does Nevada offer some of the most extravagant man-made structures, but it is also known for its many spectacular marvels of nature. Discover the 600 miles of scenic trails near North Las Vegas.
Overview of North Las Vegas

North Las Vegas is located at the northernmost part of the Las Vegas Valley and is only a few miles northeast of the world-famous Las Vegas lights. It is the fourth-largest city in Nevada, measuring nearly 100 square miles. It is surrounded by picturesque mountaintops and desert land while remaining only a quick drive away from all the action, literally offering residents the best of both worlds.


  

        
      If you love Mexican food, you have to try North Las Vegas' most popular restaurant, Viva Zapatas. The restaurant is known for its excellent service, authentic cuisine and fantastic mariachi band. 
The Galaxy Theater at the Cannery Casino is the only luxury movie theater in the city and is the perfect location for a date night. The comfortable leather recliners move along with the movie, putting you right in the middle of the action.

The best store for family fun is Rogue Toys. The kids will have a blast with all of the amazing toys, new and old, and you will feel like a kid again with the wide assortment of retro toys from the '70s, '80s and '90s.

 
Top 5 North Las Vegas Adventures

Check out the legendary Las Vegas Strip where the party never stops. 
Only 15 minutes away, the world-renowned Las Vegas Boulevard is a one-stop destination for all your entertainment needs. Catch the majestic fountain show at the Bellagio, enjoy a romantic gondola ride down the Grand Canal at the Venetian, take in one of the many shows or just enjoy a relaxing day at one of the luxurious spas. 

      

Enjoy an outdoor adventure at Red Rock Canyon, just 40 minutes from North Las Vegas.Admire the beautiful mountains and desert scenery when you drive the 13-mile scenic loop or take a helicopter tour over the park for an aerial view.

      

Tour the Hoover Damand learn about the historical significance of the dam and the astounding technology that was used to accomplish this unparalleled feat. Just an hour away from North Las Vegas, this will make a great day trip for the whole family.

      

Check out the one-of-a-kind casinos and flashy neon lights on Freemont Streetthat has made the city a top tourist destination. Take in all of the excitement while walking under the world's largest LED screen. The Vista Vision canopy offers an unparalleled light show every six minutes.
      

Enjoy an up-close and personal viewing at the College of Southern Nevada Planetarium.After the presentation, there will be an opportunity to view the planets and stars in great detail with the provided telescopes.

Tips For Renting InNorth Las VegasThe cost of living in North Las Vegas is very affordable with the average cost of a one-bedroom apartment around $760 per month.
The weather is nice year-round with an average temperature of 78 degrees.
The city has its own airport and public bus system to facilitate transportation needs.
North Las Vegas is one of the fastest-growing neighborhoods in the valley, and the government listens to residents via the Choice Neighborhood Initiative survey and website.Discover More About North Las Vegas »Average Rent in North Las Vegas, NVStudio: $7071 bedroom: $10312 bedrooms: $12333 bedrooms: $1375Popular LinksApartments with Washer & Dryer In Unit in North Las VegasApartments with Air Conditioning in North Las VegasApartments with Washer & Dryer Connections in North Las VegasApartments with Laundry Facility in North Las VegasApartments with Garage in North Las VegasQuick Search LinksBedsDistanceCostLifestyleFeaturesStudio Apartments in North Las Vegas1 Bedroom Apartments in North Las Vegas2 Bedroom Apartments in North Las VegasNorth Las Vegas LoftsApartments Within 10 Miles Of North Las VegasApartments Within 20 Miles Of North Las VegasCheap Apartments in North Las VegasLuxury Apartments in North Las VegasPet Friendly Apartments North Las VegasCorporate Apartments in North Las VegasOff Campus Apartments in North Las VegasMilitary Housing in North Las VegasShort Term Lease Apartments North Las VegasFurnished Apartments North Las VegasProperty Type LinksNorth Las Vegas HousesNorth Las Vegas CondosNorth Las Vegas Townhomes$SlideshowSQ.FT

