        The Newport Village Apartments Life
      
View Our Floor Plans







Newport Village is located in the northwest area of Las Vegas, NV. Offering spacious 1 & 2 bedroom apartments. Amenities include secure gated access, fitness center, resort style pool & spa, playground, patio or balcony, private garages available, ceiling fans, microwaves, washer & dryer included, extra storage available and your large family pet is welcome up to 100 lbs.! Come visit us today!
          









              Newport Village is located in the northwest area of Las Vegas, NV. Offering spacious 1 & 2 bedroom apartments. Amenities include secure gated access, fitness center, resort style pool & spa, playground, patio or balcony, private garages available, ceiling fans, microwaves, washer & dryer included, extra storage available and your large family pet is welcome up to 100 lbs.! Come visit us today!
            
