        The Newport Village Apartments Life
      
View Our Floor Plans







Apartment living the way it was meant to be!  You'll enjoy coming home to your spacious apartment and our service-oriented friendly on-site staff.  Wea re located in Falls Township within the renowned Pennsbury School District, convenient to great shopping areas and fine dining.  Easily accessible to I-95, PA/NJ Turnpike, Route 413 and Route 1.   * WELCOME TO LUXURY THAT IS AFFORDABLE!
          









