          General Directions
        


          From I-95: * I95 to Route 413 exit (Bristol).  make a left at the end of the exit.  Proceed four lights to New Falls Road and make a right.  Property is three miles ahead on the right hand side.  Use 2nd entrance.  Rental office is in the first building on the left.
        






